to find my friend.

360
00:33:17,450 --> 00:33:18,740
<i>I'll be back before you know it.</i>

361
00:33:19,780 --> 00:33:22,540
<i>We're just taking a brief break.</i>

362
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:39,510
