00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:21,390
I'm Arthur. Nice to meet you.

391
00:41:22,890 --> 00:41:23,930
When'd you get in?

392
00:41:25,230 --> 00:41:26,270
This morning.

393
00:41:27,150 --> 00:41:29,650
- You got the worst room.
- Right?

394
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:31,480
