433
00:45:10,070 --> 00:45:11,040
Writers.

434
00:45:11,240 --> 00:45:12,520
You're what?

435
00:45:12,660 --> 00:45:13,750
We're writers.

436
00:45:17,080 --> 00:45:18,670
