00:48:04,250 --> 00:48:05,250
Oh, yeah.

475
00:48:05,960 --> 00:48:07,000
Is that this week?

476
00:48:07,670 --> 00:48:08,670
Yeah.

477
00:48:09,840 --> 00:48:11,420
