thinking that way.

543
00:58:52,820 --> 00:58:54,320
Want me to take a photo of you?

544
00:58:55,110 --> 00:58:56,110
Okay.

545
00:59:10,170 --> 00:59:11,630
You look good.

546
00:59:26,140 --> 00:59:28,770
