750
01:16:18,990 --> 01:16:20,990
What prize do you
want to win nowadays?

751
01:16:21,320 --> 01:16:22,320
Hmm?

752
01:16:23,490 --> 01:16:27,040
When you were little, you
wanted to win the Nobel Prize,

753
01:16:27,240 --> 01:16:29,750
