782
01:20:44,250 --> 01:20:49,010
Uh, hi.
Nice to meet you, also.

783
01:20:51,040 --> 01:20:52,390
His Korean is good.

784
01:20:52,590 --> 01:20:53,680
No.

785
01:21:00,560 --> 01:21:01,520
Uh...

786
01:21:01,720 --> 01:21:02,940
Are you hungry?

787
01:21:03,890 --> 01:21:05,010
Are you hungry?

788
01:21:05,440 --> 01:21:06,730
- Hmm?
